{"tid":337774,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想換21:9 mon，求建議","createTime":"2017-07-27T15:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T02:16:20.000Z","uid":25038,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff25a38870a09d5572f8a442123c452fca01e741","tid":337774,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"個moon用咗7年，主機都換咗三次係時間退役了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打算玩吓21:9曲面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要打機用嘅，所以都想要144Hz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有咩推介呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個字，越平越好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4ad967748f3a2c3f7651c9c770846d984d3a6a","tid":337774,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"34uc79"},{"pid":"8f834a1271691c93e216885b6444ebbc3941515a","tid":337774,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>34uc79</blockquote><br />\n34uc89 gsync"},{"pid":"40bd6fdac4d4a74f868aa4dbf47204f74474ecba","tid":337774,"uid":13686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"諗住換32比9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cb5e2e179195ebcc0140caa560ee443b12a870","tid":337774,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"其實21:9 mon定係4K mon好"},{"pid":"b313f3a4951cd3e275d654d071fa1eb400d3ee76","tid":337774,"uid":6594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實21:9 mon定係4K mon好</blockquote><br />\n21:9, 4K你冇番咁上下硬件既話打機推唔郁"},{"pid":"2f95e6510771c9dff4c68b0dff0857323a4c4584","tid":337774,"uid":13686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實21:9 mon定係4K mon好</blockquote><br />\n睇你玩咩驚<br />\n隻驚唔支援21:9你都係用番4k算啦"},{"pid":"e6856f25c7d84975e1de9a64b20315332a1eca2a","tid":337774,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實21:9 mon定係4K mon好</blockquote><br />\n21:9, 4K你冇番咁上下硬件既話打機推唔郁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就1080Ti<br />\n唔需要打好激，鬥到好勁既online gaming，<br />\n但都會打下Biohazard, Rise of Tomb Rider個D<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢排重研究緊各種Mon既優劣<br />\n<br />\n有人話  曲面Mon好蝦人用  你點睇"},{"pid":"8a7bd89b555bafc5e2ecbb1026a904b10f1692bc","tid":337774,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>34uc79</blockquote><br />\n34uc89 gsync</blockquote><br />\n屌原來咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想洗咁大<br />\n如果捨棄曲面or144Hz其中一個會唔會平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2500左右？"},{"pid":"e556688c89f8d2580d3adf6bc7ef5f6e1df00686","tid":337774,"uid":25038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實21:9 mon定係4K mon好</blockquote><br />\n個人認為21:9<br />\n4K比較少用到，睇片嘅話多數1080p<br />\n打機我覺得 畫質&gt;resolution，而且21:9視野爽啲"},{"pid":"640be13226faa4164023e0156ee0cc7282b6cef0","tid":337774,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實21:9 mon定係4K mon好</blockquote><br />\n個人認為21:9<br />\n4K比較少用到，睇片嘅話多數1080p<br />\n打機我覺得 畫質&gt;resolution，而且21:9視野爽啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係依家來講<br />\n<br />\n最適合<strong>打機</strong>(平均咁講各種類，例如action games + 射擊game + Civ6戰棋 game)<br />\n又要畫面盡量靚<br />\n係21:9 + curved mon + 144Hz?<br />\n咁諗岩唔岩？"},{"pid":"6afaeee8d8d7992cc7cfb05